454
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,720
 zapravo izuzetno loši

455
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:01,280
 u predviđanju svog ponašanja.

456
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,540
 Jel' tako?

457
00:41:02,540 --> 00:41:02,900
 Da.

