 a prije njega Daniel Kahneman

465
00:41:19,740 --> 00:41:21,840
 i njegova knjiga Thinking Fast and Slow.

466
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,540
 Sad je nova izašla, Noise.

467
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:25,520
 Mislim, meni više nije nova.

468
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:29,680
 da on je isto autor i u principu...

469
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:31,600
 Koliko si puta pročito tu knjigu?

